OL,6,FMarion Loveland, Age 102, Women's
OL,7,FRoyal Naval Service
OL,9,FInterviewed 3 April 2024
OL,11,FDied 22 April 2024
OL,13,FA Wren third officer at HMS
OL,14,FCollingwood in Hampshire at the time
OL,15,Fof the invasion, Mrs Loveland's fiance
OL,16,Fwas killed on D-Day and she read the
OL,17,Fnews of his death several days later
OL,18,Fwhile she was at work.
