OL,6,FAlec Aldis was a Royal Marine Commando
OL,7,Fand among the first troops to storm
OL,8,FSword Beach in a motor torpedo boat.
OL,10,FHis body was never found.
OL,12,FMrs Loveland said: "He was a permanent
OL,13,FRoyal Marine officer, not just wartime.
OL,15,F"No known grave but the sea, and I
OL,16,Ftried to find out and talk to people
OL,17,Fthat were with him and there is very
OL,18,Flittle.
