OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: Marion
OL,4,CLoveland
OL,6,F"They did tell me there was an awful
OL,7,Flot of smoke and you couldn't see from
OL,8,Fone to another on the beach."
OL,10,FThe two had been going out for some
OL,11,Ftime but Mrs Loveland's father was a
OL,12,Fsenior Naval officer.
OL,14,FTherefore Alec, who had received the
OL,15,FMilitary Medal while serving in Crete,
OL,16,Fhad wanted to wait before proposing.
OL,18,F"He had said 'Get leave at
OL,19,FChristmas,'" Mrs Loveland said. 'I'll
OL,20,Ftake you to meet my parents, and we'll
OL,21,Fmake it official'.
