OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: Marion
OL,4,CLoveland
OL,6,F"I was devastated. I think we had a
OL,7,Flist of people that were killed in the
OL,8,Fdepot. And when I saw it, it really
OL,9,Fshook me. It changed my life. I was so
OL,10,Funhappy to have lost him.
OL,12,F"It was so sad."
OL,14,FThe day of Operation Overlord - 6 June
OL,15,F- was Mrs Loveland's birthday. She did
OL,16,Fhave time in the evening for a brief
OL,17,Fcelebration.
OL,19,F"There was great rejoicing that we had
OL,20,Finvaded," she added.
